{"tid":1543160,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(推推推推)進擊機場春袋3.0","createTime":"2019-09-05T05:47:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T07:17:02.000Z","uid":266808,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"92e89e5fcd419eaa83c89d75e7bcb261b5e519df","tid":1543160,"uid":266808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T05:47:16.000Z","msg":"之前有巴打開PO機場攻略<br />\n但無耐就沉咗底<br />\n佢有一個POINT我非常贊成<br />\n只要<strong>塞死入大嶼山交通=塞左入機場既路</strong> 大家係連機場都唔使入!!!<br />\n<br />\n駕車係最有效方法<br />\n所以有車牌既朋友<br />\n個日可以租架車<br />\n千幾蚊<br />\n幾個人夾<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7r6C8ZC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7r6C8ZC.jpg&h=cef9b343&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n在車上瘋狂圈轉睇風景<br />\n轉到暈暈地可以過觀景台欣賞飛機升降<br />\n只要塞住呢4.2公里<br />\n就會成條路癱瘓<br />\n完咗大家仲可以接返喺東涌既巴士組同地鐵組既手足出市區<br />\n<br />\n另外, 坐巴士同地鐵既朋友記得要準時!!!!<br />\n交通係要<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">同一時間</span>喺路上先可以有效測試<br />\n否則分散人流, 成效會大大減底<br />\n<br />\n詳細攻略可以睇返勤仔巴打出過既POST<br />\n[做錯左就再進化] 機場攻略整合<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dNKfRS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dNKfRS</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HTJRt4j.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHTJRt4j.jpg&h=d9bf33c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YsLwt2i.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYsLwt2i.jpg&h=096c5b68&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qcDJ4AD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqcDJ4AD.jpg&h=9343648e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RjMvKAD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRjMvKAD.jpg&h=1d480e3a&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好放棄呀!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!</span></strong><br />\n9月7日大嶼山公路上見!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><st